info.title: Perch API
info.description:
Interactive documentation functionality is incomplete and may not work as expected. We recommend you connect with a REST client such as Postman, Httpie, or even plan old CURL. Obtain your API username, password, and key from your group settings

Root URL

Base URLhttps://api.perch.rocks
Versionv1

Headers

x-api-key(your api key from the group settings page)
AuthorizationBearer (your access token returned from /auth/access_token)

Accepts query param `?type=[str]` to return only fields of the given data type.

Accepts query param `?id=[int]` to return a single mapping by ID.

        {
            "id": "EmergingThreats:Indicator-2807118",
            "title": "ETPRO POLICY SSL server Hello certificate Default Company Ltd CN=google.com",
            "tlp": null,
            "description": "ETPRO POLICY SSL server Hello certificate Default Company Ltd CN=google.com",
            "company": 35,
            "community": 10,
            "timestamp": "2017-08-08T04:27:06.350975"
        },
        {
            "id": "opensource:indicator-401c6845-92f7-4401-b71e-fc9913ac3ed3",

post.description:
Create a bunch of indicators at once.

TLP Options:
0: WHITE
1: GREEN
2: AMBER
3: RED

Confidence Options:
0: LOW
1: MEDIUM
2: HIGH

Observable Type Options:
0: IP
1: Domain
2: URL
3: REGEX
4: File Hash

Example
    [
        {
            "title": "An indicator title",
            "description": "and indicator description",
            "tlp": 3,
            "confidence": 0,
            "observables": [
                {
                    "type": 0,
                    "details": {
                        "value": "127.0.0.1"
                    }
                }
            ],
            "communities": [{"id": community.id}]
        },
        {
            "title": "Title 2",
            "description": "description 2",
            "tlp": 2,
            "confidence": 1,
            "observables": [
                {
                    "type": 4,
                    "details": {
                        "value": "fjelakjf0ndklanw00n",
                        "hash": 2
                    }
                }
            ],
            "communities": [{"id": community.id}]
        }
    ]
